code: var aggregateEvents=function aggregateEvents(events){var eventMap={};var allDayEvents=new Set();events.forEach(function(event){var eventName=event.summary;if('dateTime'in event.end){var end=new Date(event.end.dateTime);var start=new Date(event.start.dateTime);var msTime=end.getTime()-start.getTime();var minTime=msTime/1000/60;if(eventName in eventMap){eventMap[eventName]+=minTime;}else{eventMap[eventName]=minTime;}}else{allDayEvents.add(eventName);}});return[eventMap,allDayEvents];};var colorMap={0:'Default Calendar Color (Light Blue)',1:'Lavendar',2:'Sage',3:'Grape',4:'Flamingo',5:'Banana',6:'Tangerine',7:'Peacock',8:'Graphite',9:'Blueberry',10:'Basil'};var aggregateColors=function aggregateColors(events){var colorCounter={};events.forEach(function(event){var color=colorMap[event.colorId]?colorMap[event.colorId]:'Default';if('dateTime'in event.end){var end=new Date(event.end.dateTime);var start=new Date(event.start.dateTime);var msTime=end.getTime()-start.getTime();var minTime=msTime/1000/60;if(color in colorCounter){colorCounter[color]+=minTime;}else{colorCounter[color]=minTime;}}});return colorCounter;};export{aggregateEvents,aggregateColors};
